Name: Text
Text Area 1:
Visualize your AWS network architecture to simplify the process of architecting, building, and/or running applications that use AWS technology.

Note: This template gives you access to the AWS 2019 shape library. 

To create your own AWS infrastructure diagram: 
Either alter this template or click the bottom blue button to see an example. 
Drag and drop the various AWS shapes from the toolbox onto the canvas.
Search for shape names to find the correct shape faster by clicking on the magnifying glass in the top left corner      . 

Pro Tip: To automatically visualize your cloud architecture, check out Lucidscale.
